Title: At the Heart of Home — KitchenAid Artisan
Author: wavelet-director

INT. MODERN FARMHOUSE KITCHEN - DAWN

Warm morning light spills across a marble counter. At its center stands a vintage Empire Red tilt-head stand mixer, polished and still. The kitchen is intentional, lived in.

CUT TO:

INT. MIXER BOWL - CONTINUOUS

Macro on the spiral dough hook turning slowly through pale dough. A baker's hand enters frame and cracks a single brown egg one-handed into the bowl as the planetary action keeps folding.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN - GOLDEN HOUR

Slow pull-back from the Empire Red mixer, surrounded by warm clutter — a bowl of risen dough, a linen towel. Dust motes drift in the side light.

FADE OUT.
